## Inputs needed — المدخلات المطلوبة

- A CSV, CRM export, or manual list of accounts/contacts under your ownership.
- A named workflow owner on the {{ customer_name }} side (sales lead / growth lead / founder).
{% if source_passport_required %}- **A signed Source Passport** declaring data ownership, allowed use, and retention. This is non-negotiable; the sprint cannot begin without it.{% endif %}
- A primary workflow declaration (one workflow per sprint).

