## Proof metrics promise — وعد الإثبات

Dealix promises **methodology and audit-trail metrics**, not pipeline outcomes:

- DQ baseline + post-sprint DQ score (estimated, recomputed on your data).
- Number of duplicates identified and merged.
- Number of unsafe outreach attempts blocked or redacted by governance review.
- Bilingual draft count.
- Proof score across 14 sections (target ≥ {{ proof_score_target }}).
- Capital assets deposited.

**Dealix does not promise closed deals, pipeline acceleration, or revenue lift. Estimated outcomes are not guaranteed outcomes.**

